{"tid":1248360,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方社交網站上載佔據片段　認為是有組織預謀示威活動","createTime":"2019-06-21T12:19:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T12:22:59.000Z","uid":75655,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3a299503faaabb2c2c707d536442bce2a59e1bdc","tid":1248360,"uid":75655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T12:19:05.000Z","msg":"警方表示，因警察總部被示威人士包圍及道路被阻塞，截至晚上7時，灣仔分區共有46個999求助未能即時處理，需要調派其他資源跟進，服務因此出現延誤，呼籲示威人士盡快離開現場，令999求助服務得以回復正常。<br />\n<br />\n警方在社交網站上載影片，見到示威者利用索帶綑綁鐵馬、搬運大型雜物製造路障，並佔據夏慤道，影片亦見到大量頭盔和物資站，警方認為是有組織有預謀的示威活動。<br />\n<br />\n警方說，示威者包圍警察總部和警車、遮蔽閉路電視，導致灣仔警署報案室服務暫停，行為影響交通及阻礙緊急求助服務。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1464320-20190621.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1464320-20190621.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=84TmSRyL%2BgXW7nGZFnhDctDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=6d5c18eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1464320-20190621.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=32aa9823\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1464320-20190621.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a4889ee175e4354944589266e072b7f70628e9e","tid":1248360,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T12:19:31.000Z","msg":"巧京京"},{"pid":"69ffaa2e6ff81c621c4fd06f225a4d36f127d19b","tid":1248360,"uid":75655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T12:21:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces